  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Dora's off on an all-new adventure and she needs the help of all her friends, including the Explorer Stars. Help Dora complete 21 different activity-based games in seven levels plus minigames. Meet all your favorite characters from the Dora the Explorer cartoon. Gather stars--such as the disco star, the noisy star, and the switchy star--to help you find the right path. You don't even need to complete each level in order to progress.",
